# Queen of japan

#REDIRECT Queen of Japan (band)

---

## Queen of Japan

Queen of Japan may refer to:
*Queen of Japan (band), a synthpop band from Europe
*Empress of Japan, especially the ones before the 7th century, who were only retroactively called empresses
*Himiko ( 170–248), a Yamatai queen who was honored as "Queen of Japan" by the Cao Wei state in China; whether she was Empress Jingū as recorded in traditional Japanese historiography is unclear
